7&amp;h=575, https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=1534&amp;h=1150 2x"/><source media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px)" srcSet="https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=1024&amp;h=768, https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=2048&amp;h=1536 2x"/><source media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 1440px)" srcSet="https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=1260&amp;h=945, https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=2520&amp;h=1890 2x"/><source media="(min-width: 1441px)" srcSet="https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=1440&amp;h=1080, https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg?w=2880&amp;h=2160 2x"/><img alt="An aerial view of the pools at the Rosewood Kona Village" class="bmjsw TmzDJ DXqUA UMBA UbGlr  hsDdd " data-testid="prism-image" draggable="false" src="https://i.natgeofe.com/n/4a596ed0-b030-4e3d-860f-585dd74edccb/RWKVL_Pools_Shipwreck_Aerial_01-1_4x3.jpg"/></picture></div></div><button aria-label="Open Fullscreen" class="xjUSk NatTH NqeUA dZTKY QMxMQ XbEWk hswTp nkbp lIDy hUQGO gWRci aNnIu GDslh LpcJi wardV kcRqD fhCRd MYLFX RkJsE iEOQC yaNWn ZUpvj HoXXr  mLASH egFzk qXWHA ScoIf bnIxg jIRH wNxoc OJpwZ BOFPn wSPfd ofvJb bMrzT YIauu gGlNh ARCOA kyjTO xqlN aANqO aNnIu GDslh LjPJo RpDvg YYtC rTpcz EDgo UVTAB oxVnu sXtkB AAqU fctVp ENhiS kCffO " data-testid="prism-ImageViewer_ExpandButton" type="button"><span class="CSJky pdAzW JSFPu "><svg aria-hidden="true" class=" " data-testid="prism-iconography" height="1em" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="ht