_bocci_hf-1_2x3.jpg?w=2880&amp;h=4322 2x"/><img alt="Exterior of the Wilmina Hotel." class="bmjsw TmzDJ DXqUA UMBA UbGlr  hsDdd " data-testid="prism-image" draggable="false" src="https://i.natgeofe.com/n/0b2eb1c8-ac84-41c7-b925-cfa0f7f7f421/Wilmina_Kantstrabe-Amtsalon_1511-8_HR_bocci_hf-1_2x3.jpg"/></picture></div></div><button aria-label="Open Fullscreen" class="xjUSk NatTH NqeUA dZTKY QMxMQ XbEWk hswTp nkbp lIDy hUQGO gWRci aNnIu GDslh LpcJi wardV kcRqD fhCRd MYLFX RkJsE iEOQC yaNWn ZUpvj HoXXr  mLASH egFzk qXWHA ScoIf bnIxg jIRH wNxoc OJpwZ BOFPn wSPfd ofvJb bMrzT YIauu gGlNh ARCOA kyjTO xqlN aANqO aNnIu GDslh LjPJo RpDvg YYtC rTpcz EDgo UVTAB oxVnu sXtkB AAqU fctVp ENhiS kCffO " data-testid="prism-ImageViewer_ExpandButton" type="button"><span class="CSJky pdAzW JSFPu "><svg aria-hidden="true" class=" " data-testid="prism-iconography" height="1em" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-icon="view-fullscreenEnter"><path fill="currentColor" d="M6.48 11.24V16h3.04V9.52H16V6.48H6.48v4.76M32 8v1.52h6.48V16h3.04V6.48H32V8M6.48 36.76v4.76H16v-3.04H9.52V32H6.48v4.76m32-1.52v3.24H32v3.04h9.52V32h-3.04v3.24"/></svg></span></button><figcaption><div class="nhMGc uZRln ppewn "><div class="nMMea bNYiy Mjgpa dGwha DDmxa jgKNG RGHCC aBIU PriDW lZur tSkSq " data-testid="prism-caption"><div class="HXPPJ barbu IzgMt VcHIt uhSzI YGNMU cRAsZ xqMcl QtRul "><span class="hsDdd OOSI GpQCA lZur VlFaz " data-testid="prism-truncate"><span><span class="gtOSm FbbUW tUtYa vOCwz EQwFq yCufu eEak Qmvg nyTIa SRXVc vzLa jgBfc WXDas CiUCW kqbG zrdEG txGfn ygKVe BbezD UOtxr CVfpq xijV soGRS XgdC sEIlf daWqJ ">Berlin’s Wilmina hotel holds light-filled guest rooms, a locavore restaurant, and an art space.</span></span></span></div><div class="qinlA IpWvx oqZz tylGM lyWxS nWcVF UhTug PPcLh "><span class="YNujN JGtjI aZFDu rkKLh  gtOSm FbbUW tUtYa vOCwz EQwFq yCufu eEak Qmvg nyTIa SRXVc vzLa jgBfc WXDas CiUCW kqbG zrdEG txGfn ygKVe BbezD UOtxr CVfpq xijV soGRS XgdC sEIlf daWqJ ">Photograph courtesy Harry Fricker, Bocci/Wilmina</span></div></div></div></figcaption></figure></div></div></figure></div></div><div class="FITT_Article_main_group_wrapper VZTD UeCOM jIRH oimqG UwdmX Xmrlz ReShI KaJdY lqtkC ssImf HfYhe RTHNs iJVrZ " data-testid="prism-GridContainer"><div class="Kiog kNVGM nvpSA qwdi bmjsw " data-testid="prism-GridRow"><div class="theme-e oBTii mrzah " data-testid="prism-GridColumn" style="--grid-column-span-xxs:var(--grid-columns);--grid-column-span-xs:var(--grid-columns);--grid-column-span-sm:var(--grid-columns);--grid-column-span-md:20;--grid-column-span-lg:16;--grid-column-span-xl:16;--grid-column-span-xxl:14;--grid-column-start-xxs:auto;--grid-column-start-xs:auto;--grid-column-start-sm:auto;--grid-column-start-md:3;--grid-column-start-lg:5;--grid-column-start-xl:5;--grid-column-start-xxl:6"><p class="EkqkG nlgHS yuUao lqtkC TjIXL aGjvy">Cell doors and bars on some windows signal that this <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://wilmina.com/" target="_blank">boutique hotel</a> in <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/travel/destination/berlin" target="_blank">Berlin</a>’s Kantstrasse neighborhood was once a 19th-century courthouse and women’s prison. But spending the night here feels far from punishing, thanks to serene, Scandi-chic guest rooms and public spaces—a library, a wood-lined sauna, and the onsite restaurant, <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://lovisrestaurant.com/en/" target="_blank">Lovis</a>, where modern <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/travel/destination/germany" target="_blank">German</a> cuisine is served. Guests can also catch an art exhibition at the onsite events space, <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://amtsalon.com/en/" target="_blank">Amtsalon,</a> or sip cocktails in the courtyard garden.</p><p class="EkqkG nlgHS yuUao lqtkC TjIXL aGjvy"><b class="cXscX">Albergo Diffuso Kruja, Krujë, Albania</b></p><p class="EkqkG nlgHS yuUao lqtkC TjIXL aGjvy">Italians conceived of the <i>albergo diffuso</i> (scattered hotel) to bring tourism to deserted villages. Instead of guest rooms in a single building, they’re located in historic dwellings across the town. This summer, <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/travel/destination/albania" target="_blank">Albania</a>’s first such hotel, <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://www.krujaalbergodiffuso.com/" target="_blank">Albergo Diffuso Kruja</a>, will launch in the cobblestoned mountain town of Krujë, with rooms located in old rowhouses and an imposing sixth-century castle. Visitors can explore Krujë’s <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://muzeumet-kruje.com/" target="_blank">history museum</a> and centuries-old crafts bazaar before heading out to the forested canyons of <a class="zZygg UbGlr iFzkS qdXbA WCDhQ DbOXS tqUtK GpWVU iJYzE " data-testid="prism-linkbase" href="https://shkreliresort.al/qafeshtame-park/" target="_blank">Qafë Shtama National Park</a>.</p><p class="EkqkG nlgHS yuUao lqtkC TjIXL aGjvy"><b class="cXscX">Raffles London at the OWO, London, England</b></p></div></div></div><div class="NYwzQ vUYNV glxIO ilAoG HPkGR "><div class="natgeo-ad" data-testid="prism-ad-wrapper" style="min-width:300px;min-height:250px;transition:min-height 0.3s linear 0s" data-ad-placeholder="true"><div data-box-type="fitt-adb