otel</a> in more than 20 years, the best views might be from the infinity pool, according to owner Brent Pelton. Set high in the hillsides above Charlotte Amalie’s harborfront, the adults-only hotel is a collection of six mid-20th-century buildings decorated with art deco touches and palm tree prints. Stay here for the proximity to the Danish colonial architecture of the capital plus onsite pink rattan swings that’ll look swell in vacation snaps."},"type":"p","style":{}},{"id":"html16","cntnt":{"mrkup":"<b>Belnem House, Kralendijk, Bonaire</b>"},"type":"p","style":{}},{"id":"html17","cntnt":{"mrkup":"This off-the-grid <a href=\"https://www.belnemhousebonaire.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">boutique hotel</a> offers crisply decorated apartments with small kitchens and a swimming pool with a palm-thatched bar. Guests come to relax, but also for the scuba and snorkeling: more than 350 species of fish and 57 species of coral thrive in the translucent blue waters surrounding this boomerang-shaped island 50 miles off the coast of Venezuela. Belnem House can also arrange trips to <a href=\"https://bonaireisland.com/experiences/sightseeing/sites/washington-slagbaai-national-park/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Washington-Slagbaai National Park</a>, a 10,500-acre desert oasis for birdwatching and hiking the Kasikunda Climbing Trail."},"type":"p","style":{}},{"id":"06502fd7-2509-4188-83f6-e0f55df5cf15","cntnt":{"cmsType":"markup","ariaLabel":"markup","align":"contentWidth","belowParagraph":true,"envNme":"prod","mrkup":"JTNDZGl2JTIwaWQlM0QlMjJtZXhpY29DZW50cmFsU291dGhBbWVyaWNhJTIyJTNFJTNDL2RpdiUzRQ==","qryStr":"forceMode=fitt","placement":"inline"},"type":"inline","style":{}},{"id":"html18","cntnt":{"mrkup":"Mexico &amp; Central and South America"},"type":"h2","style":{}},{"id":"html19","cntnt":{"mrkup":"<b>Our Habitas Atacama, San Pedro de Atacama, Chile</b>"},"type":"p","style":{}},{"id":"00a25e52-d3f0-4d00-86f0-3f16c7e9b6df","cntnt":{"cmsType":"image","ariaLabel":"i